{
  "stem": "3949.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And finally, the time came, and we went to the train again, the cattle train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We kind of was glad to see the cattle train already, to get in there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were so, so hungry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I saw some grass, and I pulled some grass.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was eating it, and I gave some for my sister to have some, too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I don't know if that made her feel better or whatever, but once the train stopped moving from Bergen-Belsen, somehow she felt, you know, like a different person.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And from Bergen-Belsen, we went to Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was a bombed city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's only us prisoner were living there, and of course, the SS men who was watching us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was no other civilians or any other life over there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And our home was a stable, and that was full of hay.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That's where our bed was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the very, very first night we slept in, we were infested with lice very quickly all over our body, our clothes, and it was just, just so terrible, you know.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "After that, we couldn't keep ourself clean anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I developed boils on my thigh, and the dirty clothes was just sticking to it, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I don't know how to rip it off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So the whole, whatever, crust, you know, came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I still bear the sign where it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And my knees, it was so swollen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was very hard to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were cleaning up the rubbles-- the rubble from what they were bombed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got the food what we usually got-- black coffee, bread, and soup for one-- for one meal.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All kind of junk was in that soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was heavier than water, let's put it that way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it looked like dirt.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
